          <p class="model-list">POD301 · POD302 · PODCM301 · PODMC301 · POD301W · POD302W</p>
          <p>Professional series with commercial-style handle and stainless steel bezel. Same core platform as Masterpiece — shared elements, fans, controls. Different trim, not different engineering.</p>
        </div>
